simple webapp(app.py) using flask
below are the steps to follow to run the web app(app.py) on linux
1.update
$ sudo apt-get update
2. install python
$ sudo apt-get install -y python
3. install flaks
$ sudo apt-get install -y python-pip
$ pip install flask
now u can run ur web server using flask run command
source code is in app.py
4. start web server
$ FLASK_APP=app.py flask run --host=0.0.0.0
5. access ur web app(app.py)
  open a browser:  
       <ip adress>:5000    ------o/p====> welcome
       <ip adress>:5000/howareyou    ------o/p======>  how are you !!!!

